      "description": "Presenting an uncompromising example of automotive excellence. This vehicle remains in impeccable, showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained to the highest standards. From its flawless exterior finish to its pristine interior, every detail reflects a level of care rarely seen on the secondary market. Mechanically superior and aesthetically perfect, this represents a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer who demands nothing less than the absolute best.",
      "price": 48500.0,
